original_title: The Bolshoi Ballet Collection - Swan Lake
overview: The battle between white and black swan unfolds with savage grace in Swan Lake. Tchaikovsky's haunting music traces the steps of prima ballerina Mariya Aleksandrova as she dances both Odette and Odile in this definitive production from the Bolshoi Ballet
tagline: The Bolshoi Ballet in Swan Lake
